Criminal - ()
- During the day, may choose to visit someone. The visited player will be roleblocked the following night, and then can submit an amount that they have in their balance to buy back their life.
- The Criminal can either choose to accept the money offer, or attack the target. They cannot choose to do both, and cannot change their mind.
- Attack is weak attack, and end phase. Roleblock happens during the following night. Ability has a 2 phase cooldown. Cannot choose to visit the same player twice in a row.
- Does not respawn.
